column2: SELECT  s.z, s.zErr, s.survey, s.run1d, s.targetType, s.velDisp, g.*, e.bpt, p.psfMag_u, p.psfMag_g, p.psfMag_r, p.psfMag_i, p.psfMag_z FROM SpecObj AS s  JOIN photoObj AS p ON s.bestObjID = p.objID  JOIN galSpecLine AS g ON s.specObjID= g.specObjID  LEFT JOIN emissionLinesPort AS e ON g.specObjID = e.specObjID WHERE htmid*# & # < (# * #) AND  s.class = &&& AND  s.snMedian > #
